OL,3,COwners left 'deeply heartbroken' after
OL,4,Cfire damaged restaurant
OL,6,FOwners of a family restaurant in Kent
OL,7,Fsay they are "deeply heartbroken"
OL,8,Ffollowing a fire.
OL,10,FKent Fire and Rescue Service was
OL,11,Fcalled to the blaze in Aylesford, just
OL,12,Fafter midnight on Sunday (29 March).
OL,14,FA spokesperson said: "Control
OL,15,Foperators sent eight fire engines to
OL,16,Fthe scene, as well as a bulk water
OL,17,Fcarrier and a height vehicle.
OL,19,F"Crews wearing breathing apparatus
OL,20,Fextinguished the flames using hose
OL,21,Freel jets and main jets."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
