OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1774854330
OL,3,COwners left 'deeply heartbroken' after
OL,4,Cfire damaged restaurant
OL,6,FIn a social media post, The Hengist
OL,7,Fsaid: "We are incredibly saddened to
OL,8,Fshare that there was a fire at The
OL,9,FHengist late last night.
OL,11,F"All staff safely left the premises at
OL,12,Fapproximately 11:35pm. At around
OL,13,Fmidnight, our alarm company contacted
OL,14,Fus to report that an alarm had been
OL,15,Ftriggered. Upon checking our CCTV, we
OL,16,Fcould see smoke developing in the
OL,17,Freception area.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1774854330
OL,3,COwners left 'deeply heartbroken' after
OL,4,Cfire damaged restaurant
OL,6,F"Emergency services responded
OL,7,Fextremely quickly, and we are very
OL,8,Fgrateful to the fire service and
OL,9,Fpolice for acting so fast to bring the
OL,10,Fsituation under control."
OL,12,FThe statement continued: "A full
OL,13,Finvestigation is now underway, and
OL,14,FCCTV will be reviewed as soon as we
OL,15,Fare able to access the building.
OL,17,F"Most importantly, all staff,
OL,18,Fcustomers, and our family are safe.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
