OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1774854330
OL,3,COwners left 'deeply heartbroken' after
OL,4,Cfire damaged restaurant
OL,6,F"We are, of course, deeply heartbroken
OL,7,Fthat our family restaurant has
OL,8,Fexperienced such an awful incident.
OL,10,F"We will be contacting all customers
OL,11,Fwith bookings today and some future
OL,12,Fbookings to reschedule and sincerely
OL,13,Fapologise. Unfortunately, the building
OL,14,Fcannot be used at this time.
OL,16,F"Thank you for your understanding,
OL,17,Fsupport, and kind messages ` it truly
OL,18,Fmeans everything to us right now."
OL,20,FNo injuries have been reported, and
OL,21,Fthe cause is not yet known.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
